{"tid":2011602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我呀哥係香港出世話自己係黃絲","createTime":"2020-05-11T06:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T08:39:17.000Z","uid":20025,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9de7200e09412af2572627aab4d69368b3f22e","tid":2011602,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"但佢叫武漢肺炎叫新型病毒<br />\n佢話自己愛國不愛黨，香港遲早都係大陸，叫我接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔敢同自己個女講黑警既事，仲成日同個女講你曳就搵警察拉你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我忍唔住同佢講藍絲死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e1c98212d315e6820be17e1bba2561053fd3ac20","tid":2011602,"uid":125502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"c33eaca8cb8aed0dc27b97bb01bff09496b9d189","tid":2011602,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:13:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拯救佢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"56e333fdef0468347a8ebd7537fd166ef51d6907","tid":2011602,"uid":74622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"佢篤尿好黃"},{"pid":"55119ca6e57d812626731600f55861e98dccabfa","tid":2011602,"uid":20025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c33eaca8cb8aed0dc27b97bb01